@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fsursq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.21 * v2 + 0.74)) + ((v0 + 0.62 / v2 + 0.98) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.22)))
    v1 = (0.40 * wp.abs(tmp))
    tmp = 0.97
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.72) / 0.51) + ((v2 + 0.26 + v0 + 0.49) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.92)))
    v1 = wp.sin(0.51)
    tmp = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.63 - tmp + 0.43)) / wp.abs(0.03))
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.06 / v0 + 0.23)) * (v1 / (v1 + 0.24 - v2 + 0.30)))
    data[tid] = v0
